dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until order items issued (days)",
    "Time until order items received (days)",
    "Order items not committed (%)",
    "Orders with GR created later than planned (%)",
    "Order items w/o delivery completion set (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Stock transport order items issued") 
        	AS "Time until order items issued (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Stock transport order items received") 
        	AS "Time until order items received (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items not committed") * 100 
        	AS "Order items not committed (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items with goods receipt created later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Orders with GR created later than planned (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Received stock transport order items without 'Delivery completed' set") * 100 
        	AS "Order items w/o delivery completion set (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
